info.message: [B][COLOR ffffff00]Plot:[/COLOR][/B] [B] A disparate variety of couples from all walks of life strive to maintain active sex lives despite the notable distraction of having kids. From the exhausted newlyweds to the lonely single mother, libidinous single-father, bickering lesbians, empty nesters, and wealthy power couple, everyone has their own unique set of woes during the quest to get lucky.
